      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC91c10ae02b87100583ab89ec0e3196d2"></a>Washing the chain
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8594"> </a>Chains with O-rings must be washed in oil, diesel fuel or paraffin (kerosene).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8596"> </a>Do not use fuel, trichloroethylene or other solvents which will damage the rubber O-rings.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8598"> </a>For the same reason use only sprays specifically formulated for use with O-ring chains.
         </div>
